{
	"Version": "2012-10-17",
	"Statement": [
		{
			"Sid": "FinanceCostAllow",
			"Effect": "Allow",
			"Action": [
				"aws-portal:ViewBilling",
				"aws-portal:ViewUsage",
				"ce:GetCostAndUsage",
				"cur:GetUsageReport"
			],
			"Resource": "*"
		}
	]
}


## This policy basically gives finance team "Read-Only" access into the AWS billing report to support budget planning and cost reporting without infrastructure modification rights.
